title: The Medieval Islamic Civilization-Collection14 (Art and Arch.4)
description:
The Medieval Islamic Civilization - Collection 14 (Art and Architecture 4):

We have 11 titles here:

-  Bierman (Ed.) - The Experience of Islamic Art on the Margins of Islam (2005)

-  Bray (Ed.) - Writing and Representation in Medieval Islam; Muslim Horizons (2006)

-  Carboni - Following the Stars; Images of the Zodiac in Islamic Art (1997)

-  Davidson & Seraeldin (Eds.) - Architecture Beyond Architecture; Creativity and Social Transformations in Islamic Cultures .. (1995)

-  Hoag - Western Islamic Architecture (1963)

-  Irving - The Alhambra (1896)

-  Kuiper (Ed.) - Islamic Art, Literature, and Culture (2010)

-  Kuran - The Mosque in Early Ottoman Architecture (1968)

-  Lapidus - Muslim Cities in the Later Middle Ages, 2e (1984)

-  Mann - Taj Mahal; a Story of Love and Empire (2008)

-  Rice - Islamic Art, rev. ed. (1975)
